                        <p dir="ltr"><span id="docs-internal-guid-d256cacd-424c-5843-0204-ead9e8d81452">The general theme of Hanoi Forum is &ldquo;Towards Sustainable Development&rdquo;. Hanoi Forum aims at promoting the study of sustainability science around the world. It encourages interdisciplinary research that push our knowledge limits in understanding the interactions between human and environment, socio-economic growth and natural conservation in order to contribute to the development of a prosperous, safe, and resilient society. </span></p>
